question: Rachel had to complete 8 pages of math homework. If she had to complete 6 more pages of reading homework than math homework. How many pages of reading homework did she have to complete?
response: Rachel had to complete 8 pages of math homework. If she had to complete 6 more pages of reading homework than math homework, she had to complete 8 + 6 = 14 pages of reading homework. The answer is 14.
